WEBVTT

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:03.070
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:05.590
joining me today. Well, praise the Lord.

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.510
You know, I've been getting all your

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:09.190
letters. I got these

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:13.350
pictures from a 15-year-old

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:16.390
girl praying for her brother to

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:19.349
come home to Jesus. He's been wayward and

00:00:19.359 --> 00:00:21.990
he's not home. When I'm

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.150
getting these letters, there are so many

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:26.550
of them now that it's overwhelming. It's

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:30.029
all the response to the pictures. I

00:00:30.039 --> 00:00:32.910
have so many pictures of people that are

00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:36.510
believing God for their unsaved loved

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:38.869
ones and for their marriages—like this lady

00:00:38.879 --> 00:00:40.869
right here is praying for her marriage

00:00:40.869 --> 00:00:40.879
and

00:00:40.879 --> 00:00:42.910
for her hair to stop falling out because

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:45.830
of the stress from the marriage stuff.

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:50.670
I've got so many people.

00:00:50.680 --> 00:00:52.910
I thought, 'Man,

00:00:56.480 --> 00:01:00.630
if I could just train you all, if I

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:05.870
could just impart to every single one of

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:08.429
you how I've

00:01:08.439 --> 00:01:11.149
learned how to stand on

00:01:11.159 --> 00:01:13.749
the Word and get the Word down

00:01:13.759 --> 00:01:16.350
inside of me, so that you can do

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:17.550
the

00:01:17.550 --> 00:01:17.560
same.'The

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:21.710
Lord is no respecter of persons;

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:24.429
it's about how big, how bad is your

00:01:24.429 --> 00:01:24.439
'want-to.'As

00:01:24.439 --> 00:01:26.149
I'm agreeing with you and standing

00:01:26.159 --> 00:01:28.990
with you, the way you'll maintain it

00:01:28.990 --> 00:01:29.000
and

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:31.870
keep it is by getting the Word down

00:01:31.880 --> 00:01:33.149
inside of your

00:01:33.159 --> 00:01:36.710
heart. I've seen people get many miracles.

00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:39.310
They get delivered from demonic

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:41.590
spirits

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:44.190
for a little season,

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:46.429
but the Bible says the enemy comes back

00:01:46.439 --> 00:01:49.149
with seven more of his

00:01:49.159 --> 00:01:52.789
friends, worse than what he was, if they

00:01:52.799 --> 00:01:55.630
don't get the Word—if they find the

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:57.789
house is empty. No matter how many

00:01:57.799 --> 00:02:01.109
times I pray for every single one of you

00:02:01.119 --> 00:02:01.830
and

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:05.069
intercede, the buck stops with

00:02:05.079 --> 00:02:07.190
you

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:10.350
ultimately. You will have to learn how to

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:14.350
stand by faith and believe for your own

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:17.470
stuff. The Bible says that you should

00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:18.910
know the truth and the truth will set

00:02:18.920 --> 00:02:19.670
you

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:22.270
free. Now, I'm going to be your

00:02:22.270 --> 00:02:22.280
'two'and

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:25.190
I'm going to agree with you, but you have

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:27.589
to get a foundation of the

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:31.790
Word that is

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:33.630
thick like

00:02:33.630 --> 00:02:33.640
concrete—so

00:02:33.640 --> 00:02:36.830
strong that

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:38.710
when you build your

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:40.670
house on it, you're not on the sinking

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:42.990
sand or

00:02:42.990 --> 00:02:43.000
the quicksand.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.750
You're on the

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:47.990
solid Rock, and the Rock is the

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:50.350
Word. You're going to hide that Word

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:53.390
down in your heart. If you

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:55.149
abide in me and my words

00:02:55.159 --> 00:02:57.750
remain in you, you shall ask what you

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:00.910
will and it shall be done. Period.

00:03:00.920 --> 00:03:03.830
So we're going to get the Word down

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:06.509
inside our hearts. We're going to get

00:03:06.519 --> 00:03:09.030
the Word for every single

00:03:09.030 --> 00:03:09.040
person—all

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:12.110
these prayer

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:14.030
requests, all these people with wayward

00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:15.670
children, people saying they're

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:17.589
battling with sexual perversions and

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:19.830
homosexuality and wanting to be free

00:03:19.840 --> 00:03:21.309
from all these

00:03:21.319 --> 00:03:24.390
things.

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:27.589
The Word has to be a priority, and there

00:03:27.589 --> 00:03:27.599
are

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:29.869
no shortcuts.

00:03:29.879 --> 00:03:31.830
Regardless of what you're

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:34.990
going through, there's nothing too big

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:37.270
and there's nothing too small; the Word

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:40.070
of God will change it all. Do you

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:43.630
understand? The Word has to be the foundation

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:45.670
in your life. You say, 'I don't

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.789
understand the Word, I don't like reading

00:03:46.799 --> 00:03:51.190
the Word.'Find a version of the Bible

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:54.110
that ministers to you. Don't be religious;

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:56.270
just get into the Word. Regardless of

00:03:56.280 --> 00:04:00.229
whatever it is, say, 'Hey, this speaks to me.'Find

00:04:00.229 --> 00:04:00.239
that

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:03.630
and meditate on it

00:04:03.640 --> 00:04:05.990
continually, because you'll know the

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:08.869
truth and the truth will set you free. No

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:10.910
matter how many people say, 'I've got this going

00:04:10.910 --> 00:04:10.920
on

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:13.030
over here, my daughter

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:15.110
likes to play the Ouija board, she has tarot

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:17.270
cards tattooed on her

00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:21.710
legs,'the

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:25.830
devil's been defeated.

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:28.590
The Lord is not going to do

00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:32.029
anything else about the devil; He

00:04:32.039 --> 00:04:35.990
defeated him. He triumphed over him, above

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:38.469
all principalities and powers of might.

00:04:38.479 --> 00:04:41.990
He defeated the devil once and for

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.390
all, and he's not going to go back and

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:46.510
crucify himself again to deal

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:48.070
with the devil again. Why? Because he's

00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:51.469
been defeated. He

00:04:51.479 --> 00:04:54.230
was

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:57.430
victorious in every area: death, hell,

00:04:57.430 --> 00:04:57.440
and

00:04:57.440 --> 00:04:59.950
the grave. He triumphed over

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:02.469
poverty, lack, sickness, and

00:05:02.479 --> 00:05:06.870
disease. Everything. He won once and for

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:09.870
all; it's already done. So your devil

00:05:09.880 --> 00:05:12.390
problem is you not standing on the

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:14.510
authority of the believer and telling

00:05:14.520 --> 00:05:17.550
the devil he has no right or place in

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:20.510
your house. Take your authority. Take

00:05:20.510 --> 00:05:20.520
communion—grape juice

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:23.309
or

00:05:23.319 --> 00:05:24.790
whatever you

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:25.870
have—daily.

00:05:25.880 --> 00:05:28.950
Take

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:30.870
the anointing oil and anoint your house.

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:33.830
I

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:36.350
got this

00:05:36.350 --> 00:05:36.360
oil

00:05:36.360 --> 00:05:38.909
from some sister in the Lord

00:05:38.919 --> 00:05:41.550
and it smells

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:44.309
like frankincense. You can get it on

00:05:44.319 --> 00:05:47.909
Amazon and anoint

00:05:47.919 --> 00:05:50.430
your house. Go around and anoint your kids

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:52.350
with oil. I put a bloodline

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:54.550
on my kids; I

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:56.550
anoint my windows just like the children

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:58.870
of Israel did when the death angel

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:00.430
passed. They put the lamb's blood

00:06:00.440 --> 00:06:02.590
upon the door, and the death angel was

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:05.070
not allowed to come in and kill, steal,

00:06:05.070 --> 00:06:05.080
or

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:06.550
destroy.

00:06:10.280 --> 00:06:14.070
You apply the blood over

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:16.870
your house by olive oil or whatever you

00:06:16.880 --> 00:06:18.870
have and pray, 'Father,

00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:21.309
this represents your blood, and I apply

00:06:21.319 --> 00:06:24.469
this blood over the doorpost of my house,

00:06:24.479 --> 00:06:26.830
my bed, my husband, and my

00:06:26.840 --> 00:06:28.230
wife.'We're

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:29.870
going to stand on the Word and not

00:06:29.880 --> 00:06:32.550
allow the devil to come in like

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:34.629
a roaring lion seeking whom he may

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:37.110
devour. That means he can't

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:39.430
devour everybody. The ones he can't

00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:41.950
devour are

00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:45.270
the ones

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:48.430
that have the blood applied upon them. He

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:52.070
cannot devour a blood-washed,

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:52.080
born-again

00:06:52.080 --> 00:06:54.589
Christian. I believe with all my heart

00:06:54.599 --> 00:06:56.869
there's power and authority in the

00:06:56.879 --> 00:07:00.150
name of Jesus and the blood of Jesus.

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:03.710
So you must understand your covenant and

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:06.629
plead the blood over your unsaved

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:09.909
loved ones.

00:07:09.919 --> 00:07:12.189
Satan has

00:07:12.199 --> 00:07:15.189
blinded the eyes of the

00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:17.150
unbeliever,

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:20.350
so

00:07:20.360 --> 00:07:22.430
this is what I'm going to tell you to do:

00:07:22.440 --> 00:07:26.510
say, according to Ephesians, 'May the eyes

00:07:26.520 --> 00:07:28.230
of their understanding be

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:30.790
enlightened, Holy Spirit, and flood their

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:33.670
eyes with light that they would know the

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:36.230
hope of their calling.'Saul

00:07:36.230 --> 00:07:36.240
had

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:39.390
a Damascus

00:07:39.400 --> 00:07:42.469
road

00:07:42.479 --> 00:07:45.230
experience with the Lord

00:07:45.230 --> 00:07:45.240
that

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:47.350
shook him from the inside out. He was

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:49.749
blinded for those three days and he

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:51.430
was healed, and the Lord set him on the

00:07:51.440 --> 00:07:53.749
course because God had a plan

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:56.390
for his life. No matter how much evil

00:07:56.400 --> 00:07:58.189
he

00:07:58.199 --> 00:07:59.830
did,

00:08:02.400 --> 00:08:04.350
God showed up and showed off

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:08.029
in his life.

00:08:08.039 --> 00:08:11.749
I believe that there's no one too

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:15.270
far gone for Jesus to save. They may be

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:17.390
the biggest murderer or the biggest

00:08:17.400 --> 00:08:21.029
idolater,

00:08:21.029 --> 00:08:21.039
but

00:08:21.039 --> 00:08:24.110
God can take them out of that

00:08:24.120 --> 00:08:26.110
pit of despair and turn their life

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:27.589
around within just a

00:08:27.599 --> 00:08:30.510
second.

00:08:55.279 --> 00:08:57.790
Once you're gone and

00:08:57.800 --> 00:09:00.829
you're dead, it's over—TKO.

00:09:00.829 --> 00:09:00.839
But

00:09:00.839 --> 00:09:03.389
no matter how far you think your unsaved

00:09:03.399 --> 00:09:05.990
loved ones are, it only

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:08.670
takes one second. I've seen the worst of

00:09:08.680 --> 00:09:10.670
the worst sinners when I worked for

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:14.590
Victory Church in Oklahoma City. I saw

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.670
people that you would

00:09:16.680 --> 00:09:19.269
think have no hope turn around

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:22.590
within just a couple of days.

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:24.509
I remember

00:09:24.519 --> 00:09:26.670
one guy who had

00:09:26.680 --> 00:09:29.750
planned out his suicide—had the weapon and

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:31.910
everything hidden—and was coming to

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:33.949
church for the last time

00:09:33.959 --> 00:09:36.110
before he did himself

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:38.630
in. The power of God hit him in the

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:40.750
middle of the church service and he gave

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:44.030
his heart to Jesus Christ that day.

00:09:44.040 --> 00:09:46.389
He told his wife, 'I was

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:48.710
ready to do myself

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:51.110
in,'but

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:52.750
he got radically born again and started

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:54.150
serving at the

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:56.990
church.

00:10:07.880 --> 00:10:09.630
My

00:10:09.640 --> 00:10:11.110
point

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:13.590
is that there's an expiration

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:16.910
date, but

00:10:16.920 --> 00:10:19.230
there is a way to believe for

00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:20.790
every single one of

00:10:24.160 --> 00:10:25.870
these.

00:10:28.920 --> 00:10:30.470
The Lord said, 'Brandon, the only way

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:32.350
they know is by you teaching

00:10:32.360 --> 00:10:34.750
them, because you're not getting a lot of

00:10:34.760 --> 00:10:35.910
it from your churches.'A

00:10:35.910 --> 00:10:35.920
lot of

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:38.710
pastors are

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:40.190
teaching a lukewarm

00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:41.870
word—a

00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:44.670
30-minute

00:10:44.680 --> 00:10:46.790
sermonette.

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:49.509
You may get a

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:51.670
worship service with

00:10:51.670 --> 00:10:51.680
jammed-out

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:54.230
music, fog

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:56.150
machines, and

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:58.829
lights, but

00:10:58.839 --> 00:11:02.310
you walk away still empty,

00:11:02.320 --> 00:11:04.269
wondering,

00:11:04.279 --> 00:11:06.110
'What about my

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:09.590
issues? What about my wayward child?

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:12.949
What about

00:11:12.949 --> 00:11:12.959
the

00:11:12.959 --> 00:11:16.509
diagnosis from the

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:23.030
doctor?'I'm

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:33.670
telling you how you're going to

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:36.710
do it when the rubber meets the road:

00:11:36.710 --> 00:11:36.720
you

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:38.790
stand.

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:41.590
Stand therefore! When you get the Word

00:11:41.600 --> 00:11:45.590
down in your heart, it becomes a

00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:48.230
weapon,

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:50.870
and you speak that Word out

00:11:50.880 --> 00:11:52.829
of your mouth because life and death

00:11:52.829 --> 00:11:52.839
are

00:11:52.839 --> 00:11:56.069
in the power of your tongue. What you are

00:11:56.079 --> 00:11:58.509
saying every time you come up against

00:11:58.519 --> 00:12:00.430
your circumstances is what you're

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:02.030
going to be facing

00:12:02.040 --> 00:12:04.829
tomorrow.

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:12.949
Your words

00:12:12.959 --> 00:12:15.949
either make you or break you. Seriously.

00:12:15.959 --> 00:12:17.389
You go around saying, 'My marriage is

00:12:22.670 --> 00:12:22.680
terrible,'and

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:30.430
you're living

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:33.470
exactly what you said. But you start

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:36.269
saying, 'I'm not moved by what I see

00:12:36.269 --> 00:12:36.279
or

00:12:36.279 --> 00:12:38.710
feel.

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:43.030
I'm moved

00:12:43.040 --> 00:12:45.470
by what the Word says.'Think

00:12:45.470 --> 00:12:45.480
on

00:12:45.480 --> 00:12:47.590
things that are lovely and

00:12:47.590 --> 00:12:47.600
of

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:49.269
a good report.

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:00.750
As the mind goes, the man

00:13:00.760 --> 00:13:03.269
follows.

00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:07.230
You're snared by

00:13:07.240 --> 00:13:08.910
the words of your mouth; that's what the

00:13:08.920 --> 00:13:11.949
Bible says. So we've got to

00:13:11.959 --> 00:13:13.990
change the way we

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:17.269
think,

00:13:17.279 --> 00:13:18.949
because out of the

00:13:18.959 --> 00:13:21.069
abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:43.550
Your mountain has to hear

00:13:43.560 --> 00:13:46.310
your voice! You have to say it

00:13:46.320 --> 00:13:49.750
over

00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:51.230
and over again.

00:13:51.240 --> 00:13:54.189
It's the

00:13:54.189 --> 00:13:54.199
consistency—like

00:13:54.199 --> 00:13:57.230
a hammer

00:13:57.230 --> 00:13:57.240
hitting

00:13:57.240 --> 00:13:59.189
a rock.

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:15.629
How long have you been speaking to

00:14:15.639 --> 00:14:17.670
your circumstances saying, 'We're never

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:19.870
going to get out of this'?

00:14:19.880 --> 00:14:22.069
'Grandma was poor,

00:14:22.079 --> 00:14:24.110
we were

00:14:24.110 --> 00:14:24.120
poor.'That's

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:26.150
what

00:14:26.160 --> 00:14:28.150
you're living.

00:14:38.519 --> 00:14:41.590
But Christ redeemed you

00:14:41.600 --> 00:14:42.910
from the curse of

00:14:42.910 --> 00:14:42.920
the

00:14:42.920 --> 00:14:45.829
law. Galatians says Christ has

